styling rules I should keep, not because they are good but for consistency
https://youtu.be/YE0U018Copw?si=a0Au1AzUFoKt6FjP&t=465


If something has a class, all the stylings should be in that single class.
(Excluding only stylings coming from Grid, those should always be done via the object.)
Else, use the utility and global classes needed
